						<h1 class="heading--1">Reining in Global Web Application Security Risk</h1>
						<h2 class="heading--sub">The Microsoft Information Security & Risk Management (ISRM) Team needed a way to efficiently evaluate the security of hundreds of web applications that come online every year through its subsidiaries around the world. Qualys Web Application Scanning solved their problem.</h2>
